snippet.title: Defend the Highlands -  Out Now
snippet.description:
Stock up on porridge and whisky, ye bonnie Scottish lads and lasses. The highlands will soon be under attack by the English, Irish and Welsh.

Only a true haggis eating, whisky swilling, kilt wearing Scotsman can lead the clans to victory. Are you Scottish enough?

Defend the Highlands is available on Steam -  http://store.steampowered.com/app/374830/

Keep up to date with us on:

http://kiltedcamel.com
http://facebook.com/defendthehighlands
http://twitter.com/kiltedcamel
